{"tid":2342113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：終極真相持有人、銀河系宇宙國師、太陽系臨時大總統","createTime":"2020-12-27T00:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T21:19:28.000Z","uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4b25b4650252cf68501b44dd198aad25d27a1b","tid":2342113,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T00:50:45.000Z","msg":"陳雲：收到人事部通知，Covid-19 合約完結，已取約滿酬金。續約者是covid-21.  經濟大蕭條需要連續兩年的GDP下跌，故此病毒要續約。It's the economy, stupid!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCovid-19是2020年預約的員工，在2019年10月面試，在2020年1月工作，合約滿了之後，需要變種為covid-21替工系列，以便在2021年繼續工作。替工率先在英國和日本開工，工作表現良好。<br />\n<br />\n為何不給covid-19兩年工作合約呢？因為一個病毒的有效工作期限只有三個月，三個月人體就適宜下來，病毒就失去工作能力。武漢爆發、意大利爆發，都只有兩三個月醫院大戲可做，連生物焚化處理貨櫃都出埋，戲碼只可以維持三個月。故此給病毒一年合約，已經好離譜，好難為病毒公司的人事部主任。<br />\n<br />\n香港人要知道真相，只能通過陳雲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;終極真相持有人、銀河系宇宙國師、太陽系臨時大總統陳雲<br />\n<br />\n笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8ed6683fe53a14d9842c8994edf55117a60c5c","tid":2342113,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T00:51:01.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">扮燒山fans嘅陳雲糞師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n風向師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhardsell支那師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0vOfJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0vOfJ0.jpg&h=d9a57d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGVnkaG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGVnkaG.jpg&h=22e80bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8K3j6QH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8K3j6QH.jpg&h=bc059408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://